{
  "name": "TextFrame",
  "summary": "<p>使用 <strong>TextFrame</strong> 属性可返回一个 <strong>TextFrame</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作表中添加一个矩形，向矩形中添加文本，然后设置文本框架的边距。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddShape</span>(msoShapeRectangle, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">250</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">140</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame</span>\n    textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Characters</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Here is some test text&quot;</span>\n    textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginBottom</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>\n    textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginLeft</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>\n    textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginRight</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>\n    textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginTop</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作表中添加一个椭圆，向椭圆中添加文本，并将指定文本颜色改为绿色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddShape</span>(msoShapeOval, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame</span>\n    textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Characters</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;这是示例文本&quot;</span>\n    textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Characters</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表 **<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Shape/Shape .htm#Shape.Shape\">Shape</a>**对象中的文本框架。包含文本框架中的文本以及控制文本框架的对齐和定位的属性和方法。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 **<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Application/Application .htm#Application.Application\">Application</a>**对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 **<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Application/Application .htm#Application.Application\">Application</a>**对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>){\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">MsgBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n}\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span>{\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">MsgBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "AutoMargins",
      "summary": "<p>如果 ET 自动计算文本框边距，则为 <strong>True</strong>；否则为 <strong>False</strong>。当此属性为 <strong>True</strong> 时，<strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/TextFrame/TextFrame .htm#TextFrame.MarginLeft\">MarginLeft</a></strong>, <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/TextFrame/TextFrame .htm#TextFrame.MarginRight\">MarginRight</a></strong>、**<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/TextFrame/TextFrame .htm#TextFrame.MarginTop\">MarginTop</a>**和 **<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/TextFrame/TextFrame .htm#TextFrame.MarginBottom\">MarginBottom</a>**属性将被忽略。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置 ET 是否自动计算文本框边距。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表中第二个标签窗体控件设置成能自动计算文本框边距。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame</span>\n    textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoMargins</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表中第一个标签窗体控件是否自动计算文本框边距。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoMargins</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "AutoSize",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果指定对象能自动调整大小，以适应其中所包含的文字，则该属性值为 <strong>True</strong>。<strong>Boolean</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例使第一个形状的文本框能自动调整大小，以适应其中所包含的文字。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoSize</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表中第二个形状的文本框是否能自动调整大小，以适应其中所包含的文字。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoSize</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "HorizontalAlignment",
      "summary": "<p>某些常量可能不可用，这取决于所选择或安装的语言支持（例如，美国英语）。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 **<a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlHAlign 枚举.html\">XlHAlign</a>**值，它代表指定对象的水平对齐方式。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作表中添加一个矩形，向矩形中添加文本，并将水平对齐方式设置为左对齐。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddShape</span>(msoShapeRectangle, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">250</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">140</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame</span>\n    textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Characters</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;这里是示例文本&quot;</span>\n    textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HorizontalAlignment</span> = xlHAlignLeft\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作表中添加一个文本框，然后显示文本框的水平对齐方式是否为右对齐 。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddTextbox</span>(msoTextOrientationHorizontal, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HorizontalAlignment</span> == xlHAlignRight)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "XlHAlign",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "HorizontalOverflow",
      "summary": "<p>此属性只在 <strong>WordWrap</strong> 属性为 <strong>msoFalse</strong> (0) 时有效。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定对象的水平溢出设置。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作表中添加一个文本框，然后将文本框的水平溢出设置为允许文本在水平方向溢出文本框。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddTextbox</span>(msoTextOrientationHorizontal, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame</span>\n    textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HorizontalOverflow</span> = xlOartHorizontalOverflowOverflow\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作表中添加一个文本框，并显示文本框的水平溢出是否设置成隐藏水平方向溢出文本框的文本。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddTextbox</span>(msoTextOrientationHorizontal, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HorizontalOverflow</span> == xlOartHorizontalOverflowClip)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "<p><strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlOartHorizontalOverflow 枚举.html\">XlOartHorizontalOverflow</a>值</strong></p>\n",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "MarginBottom",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>以磅为单位返回或设置从文本框底端到包含文本的形状中内接矩形底端的距离。可读/写。<strong>Single</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作表中添加一个矩形，向矩形中添加文本，然后设置文本框架的边距。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddShape</span>(msoShapeRectangle, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">250</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">140</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Characters</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Here is some test text&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginBottom</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginLeft</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginRight</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginTop</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">20</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作表中添加一个椭圆，向椭圆中添加文本，然后设置文本框架的底部边距。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddShape</span>(msoShapeOval, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Characters</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;这是个椭圆&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginBottom</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "MarginLeft",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>以磅为单位返回或设置从文本框左边界到包含文本的形状中内接矩形左边界的距离。可读写。<strong>Single</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作表中添加一个矩形，向矩形中添加文本，然后设置文本框架的边距。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddShape</span>(msoShapeRectangle, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">250</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">140</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Characters</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Here is some test text&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginBottom</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginLeft</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginRight</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginTop</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">20</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作表中添加一个椭圆，向椭圆中添加文本，然后显示文本框架的左边距。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddShape</span>(msoShapeOval, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Characters</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;这是个椭圆&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginLeft</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "MarginRight",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>以磅为单位返回或设置从文本框右边界到包含文本的形状中内接矩形右边界的距离。可读写。<strong>Single</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作表中添加一个矩形，向矩形中添加文本，然后设置文本框架的边距。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddShape</span>(msoShapeRectangle, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">250</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">140</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Characters</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Here is some test text&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginBottom</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginLeft</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginRight</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginTop</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">20</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作表中添加一个椭圆，向椭圆中添加文本，然后显示文本框架的右边距。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddShape</span>(msoShapeOval, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Characters</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;这是个椭圆&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">TextFrame</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MarginRight</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
