    {
      "name": "ReadingOrder",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定对象的阅读次序。可为以下常量之一：<strong>xlRTL</strong>（从右到左）、<strong>xlLTR</strong>（从左到右）或 <strong>xlContext</strong>。<strong>Long</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作表中添加一个文本框，然后将文本框的阅读顺序设置为从右到左。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddTextbox</span>(msoTextOrientationHorizontal, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame</span>\n    textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ReadingOrder</span> = xlRTL\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作表中添加一个平行四边形，然后显示阅读次序是否为从左到右。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddShape</span>(msoShapeParallelogram, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">250</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">140</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ReadingOrder</span> == xlLTR)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "VerticalAlignment",
      "summary": "<p>某些常量可能不可用，这取决于所选择或安装的语言支持（例如，美国英语）。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 **<a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlVAlign 枚举.html\">XlVAlign</a>**值，它代表指定对象的垂直对齐方式。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作表中添加一个平行四边形，向平行四边形中添加文本，并将垂直对齐方式设置为顶部对齐。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddShape</span>(msoShapeParallelogram, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">250</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">140</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame</span>\n    textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Characters</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;这里是示例文本&quot;</span>\n    textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-property\">VerticalAlignment</span> = xlVAlignTop\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作表中添加一个文本框，然后显示文本框的垂直对齐方式是否为向下对齐 。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddTextbox</span>(msoTextOrientationHorizontal, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-property\">VerticalAlignment</span> == xlVAlignBottom)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "XlVAlign",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "VerticalOverflow",
      "summary": "<p>此属性只在 <strong>AutoSize</strong> 属性为 <strong>False</strong> 时有效。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定对象的垂直溢出设置。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作表中添加一个文本框，然后将文本框的垂直溢出设置为允许文本在垂直方向溢出文本框。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddTextbox</span>(msoTextOrientationHorizontal, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame</span>\n    textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AutoSize</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n    textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-property\">VerticalOverflow</span> = xlOartVerticalOverflowOverflow\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作表中添加一个文本框，并显示文本框的垂直溢出是否设置成隐藏垂直方向溢出文本框的文本。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddTextbox</span>(msoTextOrientationHorizontal, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-property\">VerticalOverflow</span> == xlOartVerticalOverflowClip)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "<p>**<a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlOartVerticalOverflow 枚举.html\">XlOartVerticalOverflow</a>**值</p>\n",
      "readonly": false
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Characters",
      "summary": "<p><strong>Characters</strong> 对象不是集合。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Characters</strong> 对象，该对象表示某个形状的文本框架中的字符区域。可以使用 <strong>Characters</strong> 对象向文本框架中添加字符和设置字符的格式。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表中第一个形状的文本框架中第三个字符的格式设置为加粗。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame</span>\n    textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Characters</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;abcdefg&quot;</span>\n    textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Characters</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Bold</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表中第二个形状的文本框架中字符的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> textFrame = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TextFrame</span>\n    textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Characters</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;hello&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(textFrame.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Characters</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Start",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>要返回的第一个字符。如果此参数设置为 1 或被省略，则 Characters 方法将返回以第一个字符为起始字符的字符区域。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "Length",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>要返回的字符个数。如果省略此参数，则 Characters 方法将返回该字符串的剩余部分（由 Start 参数设置的字符以后的所有字符）。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        }
      ],
      "returns": "Characters"
    }
  ]
}